{"tid":1560882,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（屎橋）呢排好多人影低手足跳閘，不如咁","createTime":"2019-09-11T11:30:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T12:33:33.000Z","uid":23574,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e5e2e9280d7abbcf6eb3b10e726832e5c6dc549c","tid":1560882,"uid":23574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:30:37.000Z","msg":"首先對住鏡頭千祈唔好認<br />\n果條友拍片影你之前<br />\n你要早過佢影返佢話返佢跳閘<br />\n再用「暴徒」「甲由」等等既稱呼話返果條撚樣<br />\n再用假藍絲account放<br />\n甚至有義士唔介意既話朋友自己互影互放<br />\n目的就係令到所有片段都唔會有人信<br />\n或者令到班廢老自己插自己人<br />\n我知未必位位手足覺得咁做係好<br />\n但我唔想班手足有手尾跟<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"8fc9f833e120ddaaa6a346c9d90ada6dae9989c3","tid":1560882,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:31:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"644d20938f0ec669e0b0cdc76eeb09e37baee20f","tid":1560882,"uid":23574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:32:29.000Z","msg":"另外我今日見到有條撚樣企旺角站閘門前面<br />\n垂低手用單手拎住電話扮等人但係係拍緊片<br />\n見到有D咁既仆街手足就要小心"},{"pid":"124a79e11cb6323a404ffbc6648e25205d1be306","tid":1560882,"uid":258370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:33:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"729d729313bba6d816cf51ba1562966d38669196","tid":1560882,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:34:04.000Z","msg":"不如是旦搵個廢老影佢跳閘老屈"},{"pid":"f5b0b47cc1d41bc880892bcb4bf7ee9f5d3d07ee","tid":1560882,"uid":14680,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:35:04.000Z","msg":"我都有咁諗過<br />\n不過唔係諗影佢先，係諗如果佢影你，你即刻對鏡頭問佢點解要跳閘<br />\n仲要好認真果種，話我明明睇住你跳你仲惡人先告狀<br />\n然後藍絲tone係咪追問同鬧佢<br />\n佢就算話係你跳你都要企硬話返佢<br />\n總之搞到佢條片用唔著"},{"pid":"6f8b762be9732b41222b599996d3090622e668ed","tid":1560882,"uid":135248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:36:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"344c8002e289a281b6bd7bfa0780a3173cb7c0ed","tid":1560882,"uid":43557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:39:08.000Z","msg":"呢招ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟手再大大聲嗌有個廢老搭車唔俾錢呀引其他手足幫拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a393b763d5b10dff55f3a865d3121db108fff05","tid":1560882,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:40:40.000Z","msg":"大大聲話佢地鐵站唔影得相"},{"pid":"bfcdc5c79bcfc034f461e782b7173eff7a1a638f","tid":1560882,"uid":7008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:42:17.000Z","msg":"跳完唔理有冇人都應該即跑走<br />\n好多時係D人慢慢行<br />\n留意4周 即時跑走 唔好停留"},{"pid":"ccca9a240e2efa823cb968683d2ed929234c5b58","tid":1560882,"uid":88167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:45:37.000Z","msg":"其實跳完應該即刻跑走<br />\n同埋我唔明點解大家唔戴定個口罩先跳，明明平時有行動都會戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae3ee0962a92864665b8e488f2120fb5c9fac6b2","tid":1560882,"uid":23574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ccca9a240e2efa823cb968683d2ed929234c5b58","tid":1560882,"uid":88167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:45:37.000Z","msg":"其實跳完應該即刻跑走<br />\n同埋我唔明點解大家唔戴定個口罩先跳，明明平時有行動都會戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:55:21.000Z","msg":"我見兩段片女手足都無帶先建議呢條屎橋<br />\n有罩就影都唔驚<br />\n無既就用下呢個方法<br />\n加油手足"},{"pid":"6a577d2e9c7d55ed5d385223fbc341405d1bf0a1","tid":1560882,"uid":23574,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"729d729313bba6d816cf51ba1562966d38669196","tid":1560882,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:34:04.000Z","msg":"不如是旦搵個廢老影佢跳閘老屈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:56:24.000Z","msg":"驚影到同路人<br />\n又影響民意"},{"pid":"a8c9d496a9002c15d33e1bee8c51aba3e5d66e09","tid":1560882,"uid":23574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a393b763d5b10dff55f3a865d3121db108fff05","tid":1560882,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:40:40.000Z","msg":"大大聲話佢地鐵站唔影得相"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:57:13.000Z","msg":"佢地唔撚驚，黨鐵唔會罰佢地"},{"pid":"45efe4bfa27df0b753486ea7f93c175593f764dc","tid":1560882,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:57:58.000Z","msg":"對著鏡頭宣傳跳閘啦"},{"pid":"28dfa6fdd6b225e82db309491a3d0091522b827d","tid":1560882,"uid":264369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:00:43.000Z","msg":"建議為區選選區，尤其反自動當選的，各區獨立設一個台<br />\n原因：<br />\n1. 既然冇大台提供可靠懶人包結論，就要期望唔少唔多喜歡睇文字的手足認真閱讀分析 &quot;raw material&quot; ．每台只處理跟各人相關的資料，可以方便大家作出明智決定，亦方便 admin 管理（移動錯台post／垃圾文 etc）<br />\n2. 這兩天有關 歐頌賢 及 任嘉兒 的討論，大家要跟post都已經有Ｄ難度，遲下區多人多時間逼，再加大大班臥底時，肯定亂到九彩，早日作好安排好Ｄ．"},{"pid":"650871e164e41d68beecff073b9b84d7a356bcde","tid":1560882,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:38:21.000Z","msg":"有時間叫大家罷去黨鐵商場 同杯尻黨鐵廣告商好過"},{"pid":"5d8f88c8d49926c7cd24dd8fff195e1577dc993a","tid":1560882,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:43:03.000Z","msg":"最好跑走啦<br />\n唔得<br />\n大家互影 自己手機 擋住自己個樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，屈返佢 暴徒"},{"pid